Compute individual contributions

Source: R/pca.R
pca_ind_contrib.Rd

Return indivdual contributions for each principal component

Usage

pca_ind_contrib(ind_coords, eigenvalues)

Arguments

ind_coords

individual coordinates

eigenvalues

eigenvalues

Examples

library(FactoMineR2)

X_active <- iris[, -5] |>
  standardize_norm()

vectors <- X_active |>
  eigvectors()

values <- X_active |>
  eigvalues()

X_active |>
  pca_ind_coords(vectors) |>
  pca_ind_contrib(values)
